OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmakeup banned              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has banned the issuing  
OL,6, of licences for animal testing of      
OL,7, chemicals used as ingredients in       
OL,8, cosmetics products.                    
OL,10,FThe government had allowed animal      
OL,11,Ftesting for makeup ingredients to      
OL,12,Fresume despite a 25-year ban.          
OL,14,FA recent court ruling said the         
OL,15,Fgovernment changed a policy on animal  
OL,16,Ftesting to align with EU chemical      
OL,17,Frules.                                 
OL,19,FBut Home Secretary Suella Braverman    
OL,20,Fsaid no new licences will be granted.  
